title: Gotta Love Lateenex | Guests: Bill O’Reilly & Dr. Robert Malone | 6/25/21
description:
President Biden whispered creepily in a speech yesterday and spoke out about "Lateenex." Terms like “airman” and “cockpit” are now offensive. Former school board member Simon Campbell joins after his explosive testimony in defense of the First Amendment went viral. Bill O’Reilly stops by to discuss the news of the week, including Biden’s gun control speech, Biden’s latest nominees, and who’s actually running the administration. Dr. Robert Malone, who invented mRNA vaccines, joins after being silenced for warning that information about the COVID-19 vaccines is being hidden from you. Former acting CBP commissioner Mark Morgan talks VP Kamala Harris’ trip to the border and the firing of Border Patrol head Rodney Scott.
